<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Password reset notification!</h1>
    <p>
      Hi! <%= @user.name %>, 
    </p>
    <p>
      We have receive a password reset request. To reset your password, click the URL below between the next 2 hours.<br/>
    </p>
    <p>
      Click or copy and paste this link in your browser: <%= edit_password_reset_url(@user.remember_token) %>.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you did not request your password to be reset, just ignore this email and your password will continue to stay the same.
    </p>
    <p>Have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>